      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "BOISE, Idaho, May 2.-The city\nis rapidly filing up with strangers\ncoming to the Haywood trial, al\nthough the case will not be called\nuntil May 3. Fifty deputy sheriffs\nwill be sworn and more than that\nnumber Of detectives employed 1y\nboth sides.\n\n\nOfficers and attorneys OF the\nprosecution are guarded day and\nnight. Extra guards are constant\nly on duty at the Jail."
    }
